data.description: Aspire at Sun Valley offers affordable new homes for sale in Coalinga, CA. Choose from 3 spacious designs with up to 4 bedrooms and live a relaxed lifestyle close to downtown and great schools. Enjoy the convenience of having Hwy 33 & 198 within close proximity. Offered By: K. Hovnanian CA Land Holdings, LLC The Yosemite offers: Spacious, open floorplan for comfortable, relaxed living. Upgraded kitchen with granite counters & stainless steel GE® appliances. Relaxing owner's suite and bath with dual sinks & roomy walk-in closet. Functional laundry with storage for linens. Convenient 3-car garage for extra storage or vehicle space.
